public boolean nonWild() { if((absX >= 2850 && absX <= 2850 && absY >= 3342 && absY <=3355 ) || heightLevel == 1) return true; else return false; }
I deleted this part

(absX >= 2850 && absX <= 2850 && absY >= 3342 && absY <=3355 ) ||

Also by any chance.What is this?
